description: Stick these stencils onto legs, arms and faces, colour in with the Pure Poppet Play Makeup range and peel off to reveal professional looking face paint type images. Each stencil can be re-applied many times over.

Mineral powder colours available in pink, green, blue, purple, yellow, orange, black and white to enable creative face painting.
